snippet.title: Bingo The Multiva - SAGE 2014 Act 2 Trailer
snippet.description: Bingo The Multiva is a platformer that takes a young multiva on a journey to stop the evil forces of Darth. There are many challenges that await as well as many bots to destroy, but utilizing Bingo’s need for speed will get you around these obstacles.
